data.value:
Pad Tie offers a powerful, easy to use solution for mapping your gamepad's buttons, analog sticks, and digital pads to arbitrary actions such as keystrokes, mouse clicks, commands and more! You can even use button gestures like tap, double tap, and hold to assign multiple actions to a single button!
All actions are assigned via Virtual Controllers, which map the buttons and axes on your gamepad to those of the standard Microsoft(R) Xbox 360(TM) controller. Once your gamepad is properly mapped you can use Pad Tie's database of hundreds of games, applications, and other pre-made configurations to just play!
If no configuration is available for the application you're using, you can make your own! Just use the 'Save As' button at the top of the window to clone your current configuration. Pad Tie uses a simple, intuitive interface for assigning actions to your buttons. Your configuration is automatically saved after each change.
